com.facebook.buck.core.artifact

Interface Artifact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SkylarkArtifactApi, com.google.devtools.build.lib.skylarkinterface.SkylarkPrintable, com.google.devtools.build.lib.skylarkinterface.SkylarkValue
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BoundArtifact, BuildArtifact, SourceArtifact
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutableSourceArtifactImpl, SourceArtifactImpl

    public interface Artifact
extends SkylarkArtifactApi
    An Artifact is a file used during the build stage. It can either be a source file for the build or a generated file from an action

    This is the interface exposed to users.
